Quickstrike:



"Ah'm fine," he said, keeping his head down. It was just his foot. "Ah had 
worse. Really." He looked back at the two females. "Th' base ain't far. It's 
one klick from here." He grabbed a hold of Cheetor's legs. "One of y'all 
ladies get his front."
